{"Id":532516,"Title":"乐府变十九首 其一 治兵使者行当雁门太守","Dynasty":"明","Author":"王世贞","Context":"今皇帝时，治兵使者任君繇。别驾稍迁，别驾坐府，俨若明神。大吏畏公，小吏畏民。倭奴扬帆来，疾如冲飙。杀掠吏士，奉首伏逃。任君当之，数折其骄。殷殷师鼓，任君在先。鍧鍧师金，任君在殿。止若春风，动则夏电。士女避敌走，不敢开门。任君令开门，全活千万人。生我父母，存我任君。入夜不宿，或昼辍飧。胄而拊循，挟纩一言。愿与同死，不蕲独全。贤哉我师任君，媪死不归，墨而戎绖。慈母令子，明君良臣。辑兵持服，舍车而徒。老弱奔走，巷哭旅呼。家斲一木，以像君躯。天祸王室，早就奄迷。何以祠君，姑苏台西。千秋万年，俎豆其间。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"1ae8b39bb507468dff82d418ee66fc5f","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6423843,"Sentence":"慈母令子，明君良臣。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cǐ mǔ ling zi ，mǐng jūn liáng chén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":16,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423844,"Sentence":"辑兵持服，舍车而徒。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jǐ bīng chǐ fú ，shě chē ér tú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":17,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423827,"Sentence":"今皇帝时，治兵使者任君繇。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jīn huáng dì shǐ ，zhì bīng shi zhě rén jūn yáo ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423828,"Sentence":"别驾稍迁，别驾坐府，俨若明神。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bié jià shāo qiān ，bié jià zuò fǔ ，yǎn rě mǐng shén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423829,"Sentence":"大吏畏公，小吏畏民。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dà lì wèi gōng ，xiǎo lì wèi mǐn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423830,"Sentence":"倭奴扬帆来，疾如冲飙。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wō nú yáng fān lái ，jǐ rú chōng biāo ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423831,"Sentence":"杀掠吏士，奉首伏逃。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shā lvě lì shì ，fèng shǒu fú táo ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423832,"Sentence":"任君当之，数折其骄。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rén jūn dāng zhī ，shǔ shé jī jiāo ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6423833,"Sentence":"殷殷师鼓，任君在先。","Rank":0,"P